Class:                  CFlistviewclass
Author:                 Anders E. Andersen <andersa@fys.ku.dk>
Superclass:             groupgclass
Desciption:             GadTools listview gadget replacement
Include File:           "CFlistview.h"



New Methods:
------------

None


Changed Methods:
----------------

OM_NEW - Filters out the listview attributes, allocates the
scroller and list and adds them to the group.

GM_RENDER - If GREDRAW_REDRAW is set this class first send
the message on to the list, then checks the lists CFL_Visible
attribute and adjusts the scroller acordingly. It then draws
the scroller. The supermethod is always called.


Attributes:
-----------

GA_Left, GA_Top, GA_Width, GA_Height

 Positions and sizes the listview.

GA_RelVerify

 Is always set.

CFLV_Labels

 Takes the address of an exec list as argument. The names of
the nodes in the list are used as labels in the listview.

CFLV_Top

 Determines which label is displayed at the top of the listview
if all labels can't fit in the listview.

CFLV_ReadOnly

 Will create a readonly list where you can't select the labels.

CFLV Selected

 Sets which labels is currently selected.
